headline: Jörg Rautenstrauch Named President and CEO of Textron Specialized Vehicles Inc.; Rob Scholl to Assume New Role as Bell Chief Commercial Officer
summary: PROVIDENCE, R.I., November 24, 2025--Jörg Rautenstrauch is named president and CEO of Textron Specialized Vehicles, succeeding Rob Scholl, who will become chief commercial officer at Bell

headline: BAE Systems to Supply 44 Additional CV90MkIIIC Vehicles to Denmark
summary: BAESY lands a $450 million deal to deliver 44 more CV90MkIIIC vehicles to Denmark, expanding the army's fleet and advancing its modernization push.
